> <i>something along the lines of what Perl 6 is trying to do (if only someone could implement it)</i><p>What, like, perl6?<p><pre><code>    grammar URL {
	rule TOP { <proto> &#x27;://&#x27; <domain> &#x27;/&#x27; }

	token proto { &#x27;http&#x27; &#x27;s&#x27;? }
	token subdom { \w+ }
	rule domain { <.subdom> [ &#x27;.&#x27; <.domain> ]? }
    }

    say URL.parse(&#x27;http://lelf.lu/&#x27;);



    Betty:hacks lelf$ perl6 gr.p6
    http://lelf.lu/
     proto => http
     domain => lelf.lu</code></pre>
